{"tid":814304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金仔來信】金正恩致函特朗普 尋求第二次「特金會」","createTime":"2018-09-11T07:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T07:46:48.000Z","uid":153236,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f817d2b563fee608be4a46e2953a468aec010bab","tid":814304,"uid":153236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"美國白宮周一表示，總統特朗普已收到北韓領袖金正恩的來信，來容提到金正恩要求舉行另一次「特金會」。<br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人桑德斯表示，金正恩的來信「親切正面」，顯示北韓「持續着眼於朝鮮半島無核化的承諾」，而美國對第二次美朝峯會持開放態度，並已進入協調階段。<br />\n<br />\n桑德斯說，北韓並無在周日舉行的國慶閱兵展示長程導彈，是北韓向美國示好，亦代表北韓無核化磋商有進展。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180911/58667423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F58667423&d=tYIKVQDHuTuwEEk%2FJ6p%2FTF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4c6b37d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F58667423&h=b167b490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180911/58667423</a>"},{"pid":"3fd0b1499c943c1e3ac6323f28c8bc510f8ff15c","tid":814304,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cc6b751011d3f64b9104d1f415e7dfe9a5d68a","tid":814304,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"食過番尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28af9e50d494159c037bb5e6483ef7aeed08b6dd","tid":814304,"uid":129658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"17cc6b751011d3f64b9104d1f415e7dfe9a5d68a","tid":814304,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedB